@Configuration
@EnableWebSecurity
@EnableMethodSecurity(prePostEnabled = true)

Security Filter Chain:
  1. CSRF disabled (stateless API)
  2. Session Management: STATELESS (no cookies)
  3. Permit All: /api/auth/login, /api/auth/refresh
  4. Require Authentication: /api/** (all other API routes)
  5. Deny All: any other requests
  6. JWT Filter before UsernamePasswordAuthenticationFilter

PasswordEncoder: BCryptPasswordEncoder(strength=12)
