@PreAuthorize("hasRole('ADMINISTRATOR') or #id == authentication.principal.id")
// Admins can access anyone's data, others can only access their own
// #id binds to @PathVariable Long id
```

### Pattern 5: Permission-Only Check
```java
@PreAuthorize("hasPermission(null, 'CONTENT_VIEW')")
// First param (null) would be domain object (not used currently)
// Second param is permission string to check
```

